A: The problem is that you are not flushing the PrintWriter after writing the lines. This means that the data might not be sent immediately to the server.
You should call flush() method after write() method.
printWriter.write("1");
printWriter.flush();
printWriter.write("2");
printWriter.flush();
printWriter.write("3");
printWriter.flush();
